{"tid":2303413,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳蘇寧出售電商業務紓困","createTime":"2020-11-28T02:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T04:00:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3694d5fd51deeb0f2a60c02f996c35f889dea4fe","tid":2303413,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T02:44:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201128/DFA37C36ZNHJXFYFG3D4WX5VPI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201128%2FDFA37C36ZNHJXFYFG3D4WX5VPI%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CiC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=b4ac01c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201128%2FDFA37C36ZNHJXFYFG3D4WX5VPI%2F&h=affd5be7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201128/DFA37C36ZNHJXFYFG3D4WX5VPI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n傳蘇寧出售電商業務紓困<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5w7boey0BUd4VQoqZ-IMB0rgVyc=/925x591/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/43RNVQ2YBFE2XI6JHAQPKKWSSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5w7boey0BUd4VQoqZ-IMB0rgVyc%3D%2F925x591%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F43RNVQ2YBFE2XI6JHAQPKKWSSU.jpg&h=1930998c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蘇寧電器多次被指面臨債務問題。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】彭博周五引述消息人士稱，蘇寧易購考慮出售電子商貿業務，紓解集團財困。據悉，蘇寧易購的戰略投資者曾與私募股權投資者接洽，尋求60億美元估值，折合約465億港元，但另有潛在投資者對蘇寧易購給予較低估值。蘇寧易購昨日於官方微博僅以「不屬實」三隻字回應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沒取回200億恒大投資<br />\n<br />\n彭博報道稱，蘇寧易購母企蘇寧電器再度傳出銀根緊絀，自集團決定不取回對恒大（3333）旗下恒大地產約200億元（人民幣．下同）投資後，消息拖累蘇寧電器的債價急跌至歷史新低，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，網上有傳言指蘇寧易購負債逾千億元，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，蘇寧電器多次被指面臨債務問題，。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"5a70d428a56eb3b99de343c00c036a080f8d7df1","tid":2303413,"uid":284699,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T02:47:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沒取回200億恒大投資</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連環<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bea5fa78789fb0afce4cb68de7ba75dec169b7","tid":2303413,"uid":109706,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T02:50:44.000Z","msg":"賣最有前景既業務，不過去中介化既環境下，廠家自己賣佢都難做得大。"},{"pid":"828d10b8f907e88d6160cc3287a0e13b3410b5d6","tid":2303413,"uid":265485,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T02:51:31.000Z","msg":"太好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6357f97ecd8e61be1dc155919ccb1a2069928e5a","tid":2303413,"uid":389,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T02:52:07.000Z","msg":"鐳射原本執<br />\n蘇寧大手買入雷射，結果都係執"},{"pid":"d6afba0037d31cda0e79b8e0f92422e26611100c","tid":2303413,"uid":265485,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T02:52:12.000Z","msg":"千其唔好幫襯蘇寧買iphone <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef0f19ceb520d3cec6a6a9f919d9fde5fbc0a30","tid":2303413,"uid":265485,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6357f97ecd8e61be1dc155919ccb1a2069928e5a","tid":2303413,"uid":389,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T02:52:07.000Z","msg":"鐳射原本執<br />\n蘇寧大手買入雷射，結果都係執"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T02:52:54.000Z","msg":"買間凶宅返黎剋死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8cf1fbac80090731d855931b18dcc5bd095c41d","tid":2303413,"uid":1069,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a70d428a56eb3b99de343c00c036a080f8d7df1","tid":2303413,"uid":284699,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T02:47:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沒取回200億恒大投資</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連環<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T03:03:00.000Z","msg":"支持國家施政，維護經濟穩定，200億不取回是理所應當<img src=\"/assets/face